From d781706c18cfbcbcd56409ebf845590415c6c2ce Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: headheadhead <b08902062@csie.ntu.edu.tw>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 11:44:28 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] add ITS support and start-up optimization

To allow the passthrough NIC initialize and work successfully in the
guest, ITS support must be enabled.

Start-up time optimization is implemented through the modification to
`devices/src/vfio.rs`.
---
 aarch64/src/fdt.rs                      | 19 +++++++++-
 aarch64/src/lib.rs                      | 18 +++++-----
 devices/src/irqchip/kvm/aarch64.rs      | 47 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 devices/src/pci/msi.rs                  |  5 +++
 devices/src/pci/msix.rs                 | 27 +++++++++++---
 devices/src/pci/pcie/pci_bridge.rs      |  1 +
 devices/src/pci/vfio_pci.rs             |  8 +++--
 devices/src/vfio.rs                     | 24 ++++++++-----
 devices/src/virtio/interrupt.rs         |  4 +++
 devices/src/virtio/virtio_pci_device.rs |  8 +++++
 hypervisor/src/kvm/aarch64.rs           |  5 +++
 hypervisor/src/kvm/mod.rs               |  8 +++--
 hypervisor/src/lib.rs                   |  4 ++-
 hypervisor/tests/kvm/aarch64.rs         |  2 ++
 src/crosvm/sys/linux.rs                 |  4 ++-
 vm_control/src/lib.rs                   |  3 ++
 16 files changed, 157 insertions(+), 30 deletions(-)

